    {# Why #}

    {% call esds.row(background="black", class="esds-row--tall-inset") %}
        <div class="escom-promo-text">
            <h2>Why a Workshop with EightShapes?</h2>
            <p>
                With EightShapes’ seasoned experience and enthusiasm, you’ll inspire your teams and spark systems work. Your team can use a workshop to:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Kickoff or energize in-house systems efforts</li>
                <li>Define your system and what it offers</li>
                <li>Frame how to form a system team and energize a community</li>
                <li>Plan how to create and adopt a system</li>
                <li>Refine how to design and code features like color, buttons, and space</li>
                <li>Develop a shared vocabulary for dispersed teams</li>
                <li>Achieve outcomes and teach via with engaging hands-on activities</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    {% endcall %}

